metadata.description: Owning 1 of the 5,000 Louise and Fred NFT collection will give you a lifetime membership. We are exploring the endless opportunities of Web3 and the NFT-world, building a whole ecosystem for community adventures and entertainment. The Memberard is only the beginning of something huge. Read more on our roadmap louiseandfred.io and join our club.
